ringen, eller forlater den kan du ogs\u00e5 risikere bot.", "- En av de vanligste feilene folk gj\u00f8r er at de kj\u00f8rer for fort inn mot rundkj\u00f8ringen eller i selve rundkj\u00f8ringa. Mange er generelt ikke nok oppmerksomme, sier J\u00f8lsgard.", "F\u00f8lg adressa.no p\u00e5 Facebook"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "bil"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5b523d3aeacc37b8b0e5b8a330451bededf1d7a177b204559703be57419b71eb"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-01T20:43:15.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Statens vegvesen er ikke imponert over hvordan folk kj\u00f8rer i rundkj\u00f8ringer."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1383049.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Montasje%20rundkj%C3%B8ring169"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/cad26b1e819d6a43c84a6cf87bfcf20d475486fa.jpg?597e741b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det er veldig mye usikkerhet -adressa.no", "Bedre fremkommelighet", "Hovedregler", "Feltskifte styrer vikeplikten", "Kan f\u00e5 bot"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "cad26b1e819d6a43c84a6cf87bfcf20d475486fa"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "bil"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["ikea", "facebook"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["styrer vikeplikten", "selve rundkj\u00f8ringa", "skifte felt", "rundkj\u00f8ring"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["norges", "statens", "leangen", "vegdirektoratet"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "midt-norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "va